{"tid":550742,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有關HD問題","createTime":"2018-02-05T04:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T04:23:45.000Z","uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e8b87f836d17ad159f467a452ea5ab03b1aec4","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"本身係舊制中五五科合格 考過幾次紀律部隊都唔得 所以上年讀毅進 今年3月就讀晒諗住駁上去讀HD<br />\n宜家有幾科都有興趣想讀<br />\n1.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ouhk.edu.hk/wcsprd/Satellite?pagename=OUHK/tcSchSing2014&amp;c=C_LIPACE&amp;cid=1385168289690&amp;sch=LIP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ouhk.edu.hk%2Fwcsprd%2FSatellite%3Fpagename%3DOUHK%2FtcSchSing2014%26c%3DC_LIPACE%26cid%3D1385168289690%26sch%3DLIP&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7029671f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ouhk.edu.hk/wcsprd/Satellite?pagename=OUHK/tcSchSing2014&amp;c=C_LIPACE&amp;cid=1385168289690&amp;sch=LIP</a><br />\nOU既犯罪學及紀律部隊高級文憑<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/eg114402-higher-diploma-in-computer-engineering/basic-information/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vtc.edu.hk%2Fadmission%2Ftc%2Fprogramme%2Feg114402-higher-diploma-in-computer-engineering%2Fbasic-information%2F&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=05d30772\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vtc.edu.hk/admission/tc/programme/eg114402-higher-diploma-in-computer-engineering/basic-information/</a><br />\nI大既電腦工程高級文憑<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sce.hkbu.edu.hk/future-students/full-time/higher-diploma/CP0245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sce.hkbu.edu.hk%2Ffuture-students%2Ffull-time%2Fhigher-diploma%2FCP0245%2F&d=bYT7YVXwPebIsydqvR%2FBuo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=80e59d2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sce.hkbu.edu.hk/future-students/full-time/higher-diploma/CP0245/</a><br />\n浸大既管理學高級文憑 (司法行政與執法)<br />\n<br />\n其實最終目標都係想入紀律部隊 所以先有1同3呢兩個option<br />\n退而求其次就係讀I大攞左HD既資格再考紀律部隊<br />\n睇落就I大穩陣 因為另外果兩科好似硬格整出黎既course咁<br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲讀過呢3科是但1科可以俾下意見?"},{"pid":"0dd810a6a46e73c9ad19da1baa19eb5e76d80c15","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9108699deb58bbd7ef3ddcfedbe4770e7e548df8","tid":550742,"uid":84212,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef765ebb7221e2d78862250d148bfa27cdc49fa9","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9108699deb58bbd7ef3ddcfedbe4770e7e548df8","tid":550742,"uid":84212,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"CS係?"},{"pid":"530ef17fa04d98210807d40a1601e8ac69f62486","tid":550742,"uid":18411,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"ef765ebb7221e2d78862250d148bfa27cdc49fa9","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9108699deb58bbd7ef3ddcfedbe4770e7e548df8","tid":550742,"uid":84212,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"CS係?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"Counter-Strike 都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6e0a462097a7fc8325e5221a303378f56daecb","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"530ef17fa04d98210807d40a1601e8ac69f62486","tid":550742,"uid":18411,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"ef765ebb7221e2d78862250d148bfa27cdc49fa9","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9108699deb58bbd7ef3ddcfedbe4770e7e548df8","ti