/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHea讀一流<br />\n一個sem先得1-2科要筆試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5ce10ec04605bb46dae72e0a702770af1d5410","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e8149f4241d2a8dffd95c8f9c18a6678d3ca017","tid":550742,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"求其一個都得啦 要個學歷姐<br />\n撚睇你讀邊科<br />\ninterview先見真章"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"都可以咁講 不過既然俾左錢 攞張cert之餘都想學到有用既野"},{"pid":"4b592f68914bd79c589c4687e3d42bc6548d20de","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4a9999c1eaafe4f346da8cea5571199941db4ca","tid":550742,"uid":39531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"電腦工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHea讀一流<br />\n一個sem先得1-2科要筆試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:24:33.000Z","msg":"巴打讀緊/讀完?<br />\n電腦工程出路如何?其實我睇佢同屬於it既軟件工程好似<br />\n但佢納入工程 讀完出黎係咪做返it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a733bd110340b5fdab1e7f1f8da77ab0b0a0de","tid":550742,"uid":62981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"讀緊你講no.3個科"},{"pid":"cb3c5e40a3e70246f464f1d7188404dbb1cf5f3f","tid":550742,"uid":165508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b7ec9a94c8dd41dd51cb8f2691e3f739ff02cb","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a67302803ecd4a6a758dfb60e80a64486babcf3","tid":550742,"uid":165508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:31:33.000Z","msg":"實話實說，如果樓主真係考入境同海關的話，毅進學歷的確好難同其他考生砌，所以我都建議你繼續讀上去拎個HD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"我就係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打有冇咩好意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"如果係考入境的話，你拎住毅進學歷根本無可能過到小組面試，因為人地perfer高學歷。而海關方面，你都仲毅進可以試下，不過要面試表現方面，及以你個人優點方面要比較上突出，而呢D優點六都係對你海關既工作有一定既幫助，咁先可以砌低其他高學歷過你既人。最後，學歷緊要，但你個人既分析，判斷，作決定，以及溝通既能力都同樣好重要。"},{"pid":"f6f86c4e60f63104f83f55c6c1731e86eab70c46","tid":550742,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b5ce10ec04605bb46dae72e0a702770af1d5410","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e8149f4241d2a8dffd95c8f9c18a6678d3ca017","tid":550742,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"求其一個都得啦 要個學歷姐<br />\n撚睇你讀邊科<br />\ninterview先見真章"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:23:37.000Z","msg":"都可以咁講 不過既然俾左錢 攞張cert之餘都想學到有用既野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩, 你都用唔著 睇下邊科易讀還實際<br />\nbtw 練好D英文最重要"},{"pid":"7edd3b231978ff8442551754775971fdeecea350","tid":550742,"uid":8331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99a733bd110340b5fdab1e7f1f8da77ab0b0a0de","tid":550742,"uid":62981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"讀緊你講no.3個科"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"巴打讀成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得有冇用?"}]}